section.information
  .information__wrapper
    h3.title-h3.information__header THE ZOO HAS OFFICIALLY REOPENED BUT WE STILL NEED YOUR HELP!
    p.information__subtitle Even though the Zoo has been able to reopen, we are at a greatly reduced capacity with educational programs and public and private events cancelled or postponed for additional months. We need you now more than ever to help ensure that we overcome these challenges. We have been actively raising funds in the community, and we are grateful for the generosity.  But much more support is still needed, and we need your help! Please consider a gift today – no matter what size – to help us sustain our mission.
    h3.title-h4.information__title Donation Information
    .information__container
      h2.title-h2 Pick and feed a friend
      p.subtitle We know the animals bring you joy, and in these extraordinary times, we’re glad.

      .information__visual-container
        .information__visual-count
          .count 4
          .description Panda diet for the day.
        .information__multi
          svg
            use(href="#multi-icon")
        .information__visual-pet
          img(src="./images/pet-image.svg", alt="")


      include ../../components/form-feed/form-feed

      button.button.button-primary Feed a friend now
      p.text-body.information__text-body Share with your friends on social networks